                    <a class="link" href="https://metamask.io/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">MetaMask</a>
                </h2>
                <p>A crypto wallet & gateway to blockchain apps</p>
                <div class="card-actions">
                    <div class="btns-connect-metamask">
                        <button id="connect-to-metamask" type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-connect-metamask">Connect with metamask</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="btns-connected-metamask d-none">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary disabled bg-secondary bg-gradient">
                            <div class="">
                                <span role="img" aria-label="check">âœ…</span>
                                Connect with MetaMask
